room_title: Escape room "Lancaster Manor" by Way Out Games in Carrollton
room_description: The Lancaster family is a wealthy group of Socialites. The Lancaster’s made their fortune through their vineyards and wine business. Mr. Lancaster tragically passed away one year ago. Mrs. Lancaster, once the flamboyant socialite, has been mysteriously secluded since her Husbands passing. Some say she moved away. Some say she has lost her mind. Whatever has happened, has piqued the curiosity of the town. You are an extra curious group of townspeople. Can you solve the twist and turns of the Lancaster family before it’s too late?
